room_title: Escape room "Cuckoo's Nest" by Padlocked Inc. in Riverside
room_description: You are visiting a friend in an Insane Asylum, when the alarms go off.  They have a missing patient.  Your group is rushed off into the doctor's office by a nurse.    As she locks the door behind you, you are forewarned.  You have 60 minutes to find the emergency exit before all of the doors unlock, including the maximum security ward.
